&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20250721" rel="nofollow"&gt;Mon, 21 Jul 2025 06:23:59 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
