&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; I uploaded explainer here:
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/tursunova/web-platform-explainer/blob/main/advanced-attr-explainer.md"&gt;https://github.com/tursunova/web-platform-explainer/blob/main/advanced-attr-explainer.md&lt;/a&gt;
