&gt;&gt; to developers. I went ahead and filed the issue for the overall API here 
&gt;&gt; though: &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/503"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/503&lt;/a&gt;
