&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20250625" rel="nofollow"&gt;Wed, 25 Jun 2025 13:01:00 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
